Third-party dependencies
================================================================================

Noxu DB links the following external crates under their respective licenses
(see each crate's repository for full terms): parking_lot, thiserror, log,
bytes, crc32fast, byteorder, memmap2, fs2, hashbrown, lock_api, lru, libc,
serde; and, under optional replication/observability features: tokio, quinn,
rustls / native-tls, tracing, metrics, opentelemetry.
